Package: scc
Type: Package
Title: Shewart control charts in R.
Version: 1.0
Author: Jakob Bossek <jakob.bossek@tu-dortmund.de>
Maintainer: Jakob Bossek <jakob.bossek@tu-dortmund.de>
Description: Offers the possibility to draw different types of quality control
    charts like x-bar sharts and more modern charts like EWMA-charts or
    CUSUM-charts in R.
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jbossek/scc
BugReports: https://github.com/jbossek/scc/issues
Suggests:
    testthat
Depends:
    BBmisc,
    ggplot2,
    gridExtra
